data.description: Premium Corner Unit with Panoramic Views of the City. Lots of Windows, Balcony, 10 Ft Ceilings, Bright Open and Spacious Floor Plan. Professionally Managed with Concierge and Security Service, Business Center, Weight and Exercise Room, Golf Simulator, Party Room/Entertainment, Sauna, Outdoor Hot tub and Pool, Dog Run, Dog Wash, Private Playground, Assigned Heated Parking/Guests Parking and Storage Unit. Wonderful Opportunity to Live in Downtown Minneapolis. Close to Theatre's, Stadiums, Parks, Restaurants, Night Life, Walkability, Conveniently Located Near Highways. No Shovels, No Maintenance with Great Amenities!
